Zlato!

1103
00:57:59,790 --> 00:58:00,840
Sakra!

1104
00:58:00,990 --> 00:58:02,010
Zlato!

1105
00:58:03,700 --> 00:58:06,070
Ne dnes. Musíme si promluvit.

